name: Lord I Cant Even Walk - Lied
chorusText:
Lord i can’t even walkwithout you holding my handsome mountains are too highand the valleys too widebut down on my kneesi’ve learned how to standLord i can’t even walkwithout you holding my hand
I thought that i coulddo a lot on my owni thought i couldmake it all alonei thought of myselfas a mighty big manbut i cant even walkwithout You holding my hand
